{"tid":1725631,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Sky News 搵咗香港一間新聞台攞料想喺美國報","createTime":"2019-11-15T20:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T07:58:33.000Z","uid":297159,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b7156b110bbb425ca50c26f2fd46527fcd51c035","tid":1725631,"uid":297159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:36:11.000Z","msg":"明白有部分手足唔太相信國際戰線，但係有外國媒體免費幫香港，將香港現狀送去外國而受阻，係咪應該出手？有哂料喺手但係唔方便自己身分爆出黎，有冇手足可以幫幫手？<br />\n<br />\nSky News 搵咗香港一間收費電視既新聞台攞料想喺美國報，但係佢哋聯絡緊既 contact point 有個廢老藍屍hold 住，唔比d 前線員工 send 去新聞部攞料，要等佢個屍腦諗到故仔先可以 copy &amp; paste 咁覆 sky news。。。我哋爭取緊既自由，當中最基本既新聞自由，要比呢 d 藍屍助紂為虐去扼殺？"},{"pid":"e61411a082a569cfe3f2542759e91df5b0d49c39","tid":1725631,"uid":119396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:47:00.000Z","msg":"可以點幫？佢係問新聞部唔係問普通人"},{"pid":"e705bc722e43d5a922db4c6277d0ebd4802dc5c0","tid":1725631,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a75a360b4bd25f9934614478525b0e6893957f","tid":1725631,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:51:14.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},{"pid":"d6409184470f988a28163a6b967f42ad6e643d9c","tid":1725631,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:52:32.000Z","msg":"叫佢contact立埸la"},{"pid":"21ac09b3c0bf7c1ef34b3d4b488d8882ed0832a8","tid":1725631,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:52:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"56013930ad3024283430db1ec22eaf9785f5646e","tid":1725631,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:53:25.000Z","msg":"立場其實係咪可以做埋通訊社責料"},{"pid":"4cbbeb9493336f9db2e28f31251980ea0f5ed5a9","tid":1725631,"uid":109115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2